### CSV Upload System - API Testing
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. LOGIN AS ADMIN (Get Token First)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dr.sharma@amu.ac.in",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### ============================================
### 2. PREVIEW STUDENTS CSV
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/upload/v2/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="uploadType"

students
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="students-sample.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./sample-csvs/students-sample.csv
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

